# This test does not currently behave as expected as described below.
# API level "21" is known in version_history.json but "unsupported", and the
# SDK does not currently respect API level status. The test gives a different
# wrong result depending on whether ":cc_component" is included in the package:
# 1. With ":cc_component", there is a dependency on fdio, and the result is
# similar to https://fxbug.dev/382560521 except that we do not expect the
# artifacts to ever exist.
# 2. Without ":cc_component", the test unexpectedly passes because the SDK does
# not filter the retired API level, and there is no dependency on fdio.
